---
const faqs = [
  {
    q: 'How does the dispatch process work?',
    a: 'Once you sign up, we assign you a dedicated dispatcher who learns your preferences — your lanes, preferred cargo types, and target rates. They search the load boards, negotiate directly with brokers, and send you loads to approve before booking. You stay in control.',
  },
  {
    q: 'What is your commission rate?',
    a: 'We charge 5% of gross revenue for most truck types (Dry Van, Flatbed, Reefer, Step Deck, Conestoga). Hotshot is 7% due to the higher volume of smaller loads. There are no setup fees, no monthly minimums, and no hidden charges.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Do I need an active MC number to get started?',
    a: 'Yes. Requirements vary by truck type — Dry Van only needs 1 month of active MC, while Flatbed, Reefer, Hotshot, Step Deck, and Conestoga require 6 months. This protects both you and our broker relationships.',
  },
  {
    q: 'How quickly can I get set up?',
    a: 'Most carriers are fully onboarded within 24-48 hours. After your free setup call, we verify your credentials, set up your profile, and your dispatcher gets to work finding your first loads right away.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Do you handle my DOT compliance and paperwork?',
    a: 'Yes. Our document management team handles permits, BOLs, rate confirmations, and compliance filings. We also track renewal deadlines for your operating authority and insurance so you never fall out of compliance.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Can you help me get paid faster?',
    a: 'Absolutely. We have freight factoring partnerships that can get you paid in as little as 24 hours instead of waiting 30-60 days. We also follow up aggressively with brokers on outstanding invoices.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Is there a long-term contract?',
    a: 'No long-term contract. You can cancel at any time. Our goal is to earn your business every single week by delivering results — not to lock you into a commitment you can\'t get out of.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Do you dispatch for fleets or only owner-operators?',
    a: 'Both. We work with solo owner-operators and small-to-mid-size fleets. For fleets, we assign multiple dispatchers and scale our services to match your operational needs.',
  },
];
---

<section class="bg-white py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-12 text-center">
      <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-orange-500">
        FAQ
      </p>
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl">
        Common Questions
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
        Everything you need to know before getting started with us.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Accordion -->
    <div class="divide-y divide-gray-200 border-y border-gray-200">
      {
        faqs.map((faq) => (
          <details class="group">
            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between py-5">
              <span class="pr-4 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">{faq.q}</span>
              <span class="shrink-0 text-gray-400 transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-45">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4.5v15m7.5-7.5h-15" />
                </svg>
              </span>
            </summary>
            <div class="pb-5 pr-8">
              <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">{faq.a}</p>
            </div>
          </details>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
